name: Sky Tracers
description:
Jump over rooftops, scale sky scrapers and fight off hostile robots as you master the almost infinite depth of rocket parkour. Find and carve your very own path through challenging courses in a frantic multiplayer race.Features:
  • Race against other players and compete for the fastest time on each stage.
  • Additional game modes to be announced.
  • Customize your character.
  • Hang out with other players in social areas between matches
More info coming soon!
